'''Shirmar Base''' was a staging area and a processing center built on the [[Bespin/Legends|Bespin]] [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Drudonna]].

It was constructed by the [[Ugnaught/Legends|Ugnaughts]] to allow them easier access to [[Velser's Ring/Legends|Velsor's Ring]], where they maintained mining operations.

